  "title": "Contracts Manager (HDB/Condo/Landed Projects)",
  "description": "<ul><li>Manage contracts, procurement, and claims with contractors and suppliers.</li><li>Ensure compliance with contractual obligations and project requirements.</li><li>Resolve disputes and implement cost control measures.</li><li>Negotiate terms and conditions to minimize risk and maximize value for the company.</li></ul><p>Requirements:</p><ul><li>Degree in Construction/Quantity Surveying or equivalent</li><li>At least 5 years’ experience handling contracts for <strong>HDB, Condo, and Landed projects.</strong></li><li>Strong knowledge of construction law and contract management.</li><li>Excellent negotiation, analytical, and risk assessment skills.</li></ul><p>If you are keen to apply for the position, kindly email your detailed resume in<strong> MS Word </strong>to <strong>hr@recruit-expert.com</strong></p><p>Please note that only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p><p>For more job opportunities, please visit our website at <a href=\"http://www.recruit-expert.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>www.recruit-expert.com</strong></a></p><p>EA Licence: 19C9701</p><p>Registration: R1326740</p>",
